        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="主机选择及动态建站"><a href="#主机选择及动态建站" class="headerlink" title="主机选择及动态建站"></a>主机选择及动态建站</h1><h2 id="一些废话"><a href="#一些废话" class="headerlink" title="一些废话"></a>一些废话</h2><p>很喜欢markdown的写作方式，但无奈hexo里面坑真的很多，自己又不是什么前端大神，所以选择做双网站，静态自己玩+动态展示用</p><h2 id="主机信息"><a href="#主机信息" class="headerlink" title="主机信息"></a>主机信息</h2><ul><li><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/act/campus?fromSource=gwzcw.3180703.3180703.3180703&amp;utm_id=gwzcw.3180703.3180703.3180703" target="_blank" rel="noopener">腾讯云学生优惠</a>：120/年，云服务器1核+2G+50G；非学生为128；域名优惠仅限新用户</li><li><a href="https://www.didiyun.com/activity.html#hotZone" target="_blank" rel="noopener">滴滴云DC2</a>：68/年(新人-15)，云服务器1核+2G+40G</li><li><a href="https://cloud.baidu.com/campaign/Annualceremony-2020/index.html?track=cp:nsem|pf:pc|pp:npinzhuan-biaoti|pu:wenzineirong|ci:2020ndsd|kw:2180026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度云</a>：84/年，云服务器1核+1G+40G；17/6个月，云虚拟主机256M+3G；域名10元左右</li><li><a href="https://www.aliyun.com/acts/product?spm=5176.12825654.gzwmvexct.d118.3dbd2c4azZO1bx&amp;scm=20140722.1411.7.1434&amp;aly_as=eSHlm_Ho" target="_blank" rel="noopener">阿里云</a>：89/年，云服务器1核+2G+40G；<a href="https://promotion.aliyun.com/ntms/act/campus2018.html?spm=5176.8112568.420890.3.11589ed5FzrwBS&amp;aly_as=Cfuy3onc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">云翼计划</a>9.5一个月；疫情期间学生免费一年</li></ul><h2 id="建站"><a href="#建站" class="headerlink" title="建站"></a>建站</h2><ul><li>主机：阿里云/ECS 2核4G/免费</li><li>域名：阿里云1元域名，备案</li><li>预装宝塔面板linux</li><li><a href="https://market.aliyun.com/products/53690006/cmjj015022.html?spm=5176.2020520132.101.2.4fa57218ameCKihttps://market.aliyun.com/products/53690006/cmjj015022.html?spm=5176.2020520132.101.2.4fa57218ameCKi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">配置放行端口</a></li><li>访问宝塔面板</li><li>安装LAMP</li><li>安装wordpress</li></ul><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');           